{{核武器}}
'''简易核装置'''（英语：Improvised nuclear devices）是从[[拥核国家|拥核国家]]购买、盗窃或以其他方式得到的理论上的非法的[[核武器|核武器]]，或是恐怖组织用非法获取的可裂变物质制造的可产生[[核爆炸|核爆炸]]的武器。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Student Guide Improvised Nuclear Device (IND) Modeling and Response Planning: National Capital Region |url=https://responder.llnl.gov/content/assets/docs/training/SG-NCR-Awareness-Briefing.pdf |format=PDF |publisher= |accessdate=2020-10-11 |date= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011163628/https://responder.llnl.gov/content/assets/docs/training/SG-NCR-Awareness-Briefing.pdf |archivedate=2020-10-11 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Improvised Nuclear Device Response and Recovery |url=https://www.fema.gov/media-library-data/20130726-1919-25045-0618/communicating_in_the_immediate_aftermath__final_june_2013_508_ok.pdf |format=PDF |publisher=[[聯邦緊急事務管理署|FEMA]] |accessdate=2020-10-11 |date= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011163934/https://www.fema.gov/media-library-data/20130726-1919-25045-0618/communicating_in_the_immediate_aftermath__final_june_2013_508_ok.pdf |archivedate=2020-10-11 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Improvised Nuclear Device Infographic |url=https://emergency.cdc.gov/radiation/pdf/infographic_improvised_nuclear_device.pdf |format=PDF |publisher=CDC |accessdate=2019-06-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616113417/https://emergency.cdc.gov/radiation/pdf/infographic_improvised_nuclear_device.pdf |archivedate=2019-06-16 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>简易核装置可通过购买得到，也可以用窃得的武器部件制造，或使用核材料（[[钚|钚]]、[[铀|铀]]或高[[浓缩铀|浓缩铀]]）从零开始制作。 一次成功的爆炸将导致灾难性的人员伤亡、基础设施损毁以及大面积的[[核污染|核污染]]。

== 类型 ==
其中一种简易核装置袭击可能是恐怖分子投放放射性散布装置，即所谓的“[[脏弹|脏弹]]”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=“Dirty Bombs”: Technical Background, Attack Prevention and Response, Issues for Congress |url=https://fas.org/sgp/crs/nuke/R41890.pdf |format=PDF |first=Jonathan |last=Medalia |accessdate=2015-11-23 |date=2011-06-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123042823/https://fas.org/sgp/crs/nuke/R41890.pdf |archivedate=2015-11-23 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Backgrounder on Dirty Bombs |url=https://www.nrc.gov/reading-rm/doc-collections/fact-sheets/fs-dirty-bombs.pdf |format=PDF |publisher=NRC |accessdate=2015-08-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801054957/https://www.nrc.gov/reading-rm/doc-collections/fact-sheets/fs-dirty-bombs.pdf |archivedate=2015-08-01|deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Dirty Bombs |url=http://faculty.uml.edu/bleblanc/44.212/pdf/Microsoft_PowerPoint_-_DirtyBombs.pdf|format=PDF |publisher= |accessdate=2017-04-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170424002204/http://faculty.uml.edu/bleblanc/44.212/pdf/Microsoft_PowerPoint_-_DirtyBombs.pdf |archivedate=2017-04-24 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>放射性散布装置不会引发核爆炸，而是使用化学炸药来传播有害的辐射。它可能会在城市地区造成严重的经济混乱和恐慌，而不会造成大量人员死伤。由于这些物质在工业、农业和医药领域很常用，恐怖分子很容易能获得这些材料。

[[纳米技术|纳米技术]]理论上可用于开发小型激光触发的纯热核武器，这种武器比常规核武器更容易生产，并可用于恐怖袭击。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mini-nukes and mosquito-like robot weapons being primed for future warfare |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2017/03/17/mini-nukes-and-inspect-bot-weapons-being-primed-for-future-warfare.html |first=Jeff |last=Daniels |publisher=[[全国广播公司商业频道|CNBC]] |accessdate=2020-10-11 |date=2017-03-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011165454/https://www.cnbc.com/2017/03/17/mini-nukes-and-inspect-bot-weapons-being-primed-for-future-warfare.html |archivedate=2020-10-11 |deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>

== 设计考虑 ==
从头开始制造的简易核装置很可能是[[核武器设计方案#枪式|枪式]]的，这样设计和制造起来相当容易（然而需要高[[濃縮鈾|濃縮鈾]]）。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Homeland Security Planning Scenarios |url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/security/ops/hsc-scen-1.htm |accessdate=2020-10-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011165804/https://www.globalsecurity.org/security/ops/hsc-scen-1.htm |archivedate=2020-10-11|deadurl=no |language=en}}</ref>

由于[[裂变|裂变]]不完全，简易核装置可能会导致更多的[[放射性落塵|放射性落塵]]——由于对[[弹芯|弹芯]]进行[[过度工程化|过度工程化]]（使其更重以确保裂变至少部分发生）；使用[[核武器设计方案#枪式|枪式]]设计；或者由于{{Le|提前引爆|Fizzle (nuclear explosion)}}（工程或制造错误，使释放 能量降低）——而且可能在地面而不是在[[空中爆炸|空中爆炸]]，导致地面目标受到大量辐射并被卷入[[蘑菇云|蘑菇云]]。

